channel.title: Noobscape and eclipse start up trouble
channel.description:
I figured out how to start a new java project in eclipse. Then I put Noobscape 317 on it. The next thing I have to do is look at the JRE system library, and I can't find the lib file that has what I need. What I need is xpp3 and extreme jar files.
Pretty much I can't find the way to run the server through eclipse.
